## 📌 10. Service vs Image (Very Important)

| Concept | Example |
| ------- | ------- |
| Service | web     |
| Image   | nginx   |

### Correct exec

```
docker compose exec web sh
```

---

## 📌 11. Ubuntu Container Setup

### Add in compose file

```yaml
  ubuntu:
    image: ubuntu
    stdin_open: true
    tty: true
```

### Run

```
docker compose up -d
```

### Enter container

```
docker compose exec ubuntu bash
```

---

## 📌 12. Important Concepts Learned

* Docker Compose depends on file naming convention
* Containers must be running for exec
* Service name ≠ image name
* Network issues affect image pulling
* Foreground vs detached mode

